      when "4-4-1-a-ii-p"
        | Inflection is not done in the genitive singular masculine on monosyllabic adjectives ending in #[i -ch(t)] (except #[i bocht]), e.g., #[i beacht] #[+tl exact], #[i caoch] #[+tl blind], #[i déach] #[+tl dual], #[i fliuch] #[+tl wet], #[i lách] #[+tl pleasant], #[i moch] #[+tl early], #[i nocht] #[+tl naked].
      when "4-4-1-a-ii-p-sample1"
        | They had to hold the festival at the end of the #[b wet] summer.
      when "4-4-1-a-ii-p-sample2"
