      when "4-4-1-a-iii-p-sample1"
        | I would like to speak to the parents of the #[b quiet] boy.
      when "4-4-1-a-iii-p-sample2"
        | Everyone was in favor of the #[b industrial] campaign.
      when "4-4-1-a-iv-p"
        | Inflection is not done in the genitive singular masculine on monosyllabic adjectives ending in double consonants (except #[i dall] #[+tl blind], #[i donn] #[+tl brown], #[i fionn] #[+tl fair]), e.g., #[i cearr] #[+tl wrong], #[i corr] #[+tl odd], #[i gann] #[+tl scarce], #[i gearr] #[+tl short], #[i mall] #[+tl slow], #[i teann] #[+tl tight], #[i toll] #[+tl hollow].
      when "4-4-1-a-iv-p-sample1"
        | The price of #[b scarce] food is rising every day.
