      when "4-10-p"
        | The demonstrative adjectives are #[i seo] #[+tl this], #[i sin] #[+tl that], #[i siúd] #[+tl that over there] and #[i úd] #[+tl that over there]. (Although #[i seo], #[i sin] and #[i siúd] are demonstrative pronominals, they are often referred to as demonstrative adjectives.)
